  Te7 chap8 ChiuN 
  Li2 sian-siN bo5 tai7-chi3 ti7 pun2 hiuN-sia7 kong2 to7-li2; tu2-gu7 him-bou7 to7-li2 e5 chhu3-piN kau3 le2-pai3-jit8 chiu7 chhiaN2 in kau3 i-e5 ke-lai7 thiaN i kong2 Seng3-chheh, i ka3-si7 lang5 bo5 ia3-lan2. 
  In-ui7 chhu3 se3-keng lang5 thai3 che7, siong5-siong5 ti7 hiuN-sia7 e5 tiong-kan toa7 te7-tiuN5 teh kong2 to7-li2. Tak8 lang5 ka-ki7 gia5 i2-liau5 lai5 che7 teh thiaN i kong2; hiuN-sia7 e5 lang5 long2 chai i chai7-cha2 an2-chaiN2-iuN7 put-siau3; au7--lai5 an2-chaiN2-iuN7 hoan2-hoe2 ke2-piN3. Sou2-i2 bo5 beh thiaN i e5 lang5 si7 chio2-chio2. I e5 to7-li2 sui-jian5 kap se3-siok8 bo5 saN-tang5, tau3-ti2 kap lang5 ong2-lai5, si7 eng7 le2-mau7 sio khoan2-thai7. Iu7-koh i kong2 to7-li2 e5 si5 cheng3-chong ho5-peng5, sou2-i2 be7 ti3-kau3 kap lang5 oan-ke, tok8-tok8 hou7 lang5 hoaN-hi2 hang5-hok8. I boe7 kong2 i2-cheng5 tai7-seng khou2-khng3 lang5 cheng7-cheng7 thiaN, ki3-jian5 kong2-liau2 hoaN-hi2 hou7 lang5 siong5-se3 mng7. ThiaN i kong2 e5 lang5 sim-koaN bo5 siang7-khoan2. U7-e5 kong2,“Chin-chiaN3-si7 ho2 e5 to7-li2 kho2-kham kiu3 lang5;”u7-e5 kong2,“Che m7-chai si7 sim2-mih8 to7-li2, lan2 Tiong-kok tui3 kou2-cha2 i2-lai5 long2 bo5, thiaN i beh siaN2-thai7? Long2 si7 chit ho7 e5 oe7 kong2 be7-tit chin7.” 
  Tiong-kan u7 chit8-e5 lau7-lang5 kong2,“Na7-si7 to7-li2, chiu7 tioh8 chin3-cheng5, m7-si7 to7-li2, chiu7 tioh8 the3-au7,”chiu7 tui3 Li2 sian-siN kong2, “Thang mng7 to7-li2 a2 m7-thang?”Li2 sian-siN kong2,“Thang thang.” 
  Lau7-lang5 chiu7 mng7 i kong2,“ThiN-te7 hiah toa7 beh thai3-e7 bo5 sin5, chiau3 sian-siN e5 oe7, kiam2 m7-si7 in2-chhoa7 lang5 bo5 keng3 sin5-mah?” 
  Li2 sian-siN in3 i kong2,“Goa2 m7-si7 kong2 bo5 sin5; na7 bo5 sin5 beh thai3 u7 thiN-te7 ban7-mih8? Goa2 iah8 m7-si7 in2-chhoa7 lang5 bo5 keng3 sin5; goa2 sou2 kong2 e5 to7-li2 cho3 iau3-kin2-e5 chiu7-si7 keng3 sin5. Chong2-si7 sin5 u7 chin u7 ke2; ho7-cho3 chin-sin5 chiu7-si7 tok8-it bu5-ji7, toa7 Chu2-chaiN2 e5 Siong7-te3, lang5 long2 eng-kai tioh8 seng5-sim lai5 ai3 keng3 I. Che chiaN3-si7 lang5 e5 toa7 e5 toa7 pun2-hun7, chhin-chhiuN7 kong2 thiN-te7 bo5 nng7 e5 jit8, peh-siN3 bo5 nng7 e5 ong5; m7-si7 kong2 bo5 jit8, bo5 ong5; si7 kong2 u7 chit8-e5 bo5 nng7 e5 nia7-nia7. Goa2 kong2 Siong7-te3 tok8-it bu5-ji7 iah8 si7 an2-ni.” 
  Lau7-lang5 mng7,“Sian-siN an2-chaiN2-iuN7 chai se3-siok8 sou2 keng3 e5 sin5 long2 si7 ke2--e5 mah?” 
  In3-kong2,“Se3-siok8 sou2 keng3 e5 sin5 hoan7 e7 khoaN3-kiN3--e5 chiu7-si7 thou5 cho7, chha5 tiau lang5 e5 chhiu2 sou2 cho3 e5 siong7 si7 gai5 mih8. Chiong kek8 leng5-lai7 e5 lang5 khi3 pai3 hit-ho7 bo5 leng5-khi3 e5 mih8, si7 ha7-chian7 kau3 kek8. Hoan7 be7 khoaN3-kiN3 e5, chiu7-si7 cheng5 tai7 si2-liau2 e5 lang5; chhin-chhiuN7 TiuN Gi5 chheng-hou cho3 Giok8-te3; Lau5 Tiong5-seng chheng-hou cho3 Chin-hu2; Bun5 Thai3-su chheng-hou cho3 Lui5-chou2; Ng5 Hui-hou2 chheng-hou cho3 Tong-gak8; Koan-kong chheng-hou cho3 Hiap8-thian Tai7-te3; Tio7 Kong-beng5 chheng-hou cho3 Chai5-sin5. Chhin-chhiuN7 chit chit8 lui7 long2 si7 lang5, liah8 i cho3 sin5, cho3 Siong7-te3, lai5 keng3-pai3-i, m7-na7 ka-ti7 hian2-chhut gu5-gong7 ou-am3, koh toa7-toa7 tek-choe7--tioh8 chin Sin5 Siong7-te3.” 
  Lau7-lang5 mng7,“Ngou2-te3, Giok8-te3, Goau5-thian7, Chi2-bi5, hiah e5 kiam2 thang kong2 long2 m7-si7 Siong7-te3 mah?” 
  In3 kong2,“Long2 m7-si7, si7 lang5 sou2 phah-sng3 sou2 chhong3-cho7; hek8-si7 jin5-kun sou2 thek-hong, hek8-si7 hit kau3-hoe7 ka-ti7 hong--e5, chheng i cho3 Siong7-te3, si7 lam7-sam2 chheng-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 mia5.” 
  Lau7-lang5 mng7,“Put8 kap chiong3 Phou-sat si7 lang5 a2-si7 sin5?” 
  In3 kong2,“Long2 si7 lang5, m7-si7 Tiong-kok lang5, si7 Se-kok lang5. ” 
  Lau7-lang5 mng7,“Hiah-e5 Phou-sat i2-keng siu7 thek-hong, kiam2 thang kong2 m7-si7 sin5 mah?” 
  In3-kong2,“Hong-sin5 hit ho7 se3-siok8 kai3 bo5 iaN2, kai3 sia5, kai3 phaiN2. TaN Siong7-te3 si7 cho3 thiN-te7 lang5 mih8 e5 toa7 Chu2-chaiN2, bo5 sou2 be7-e7, bo5 sou2 m7-chai, sng3-si7 tok8-it e5 chin Sin5. Hou7 Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 e5 sio2-khoa2 lang5 beh thai3-e7 hong lang5 cho3 Siong7-te3 leh? Beh thai3-e7 hou7 lang5 hong-cho3 Siong7-te3 leh?” 
  Lau7-lang5 mng7,“Hou7 lang5 hong cho3 sin5 e5, tai7-khai3 long2-si7 u7 kong-lo5 ti7 kok-nih8, u7 iu-tek ti7 lang5 tau, nia3 thang khi3-choat8 pang3-sak--i?” 
  In3 kong2,“Goa2 m7-si7 kong2 i bo5 kong-lo5, bo5 in-tek; iah8 m7-si7 ka3 lang5 tioh8 khi3-choat8 i. Na7-u7 ho2 e5 ka3-si7 tioh8 sun7-than3, na7-u7 ho2 e5 tek-heng7 tioh8 oh8--i. I-e5 kong-lo5 in-tek m7-thang be7-ki3-tit; siaN2-su7 khi3-choat8 pang3-sak i leh? Goa2 tok8-tok8 kong2 i m7-si7 Siong7-te3, m7-si7 sin5, si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 chhong3-cho7 e5 lang5. Liah8 i cho3 sin5, lai5 cho3 i, pai3--i, kiu5--i si7 hoan7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 hoat-tou7, jia2-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 siu7-khi3.” 
  Phi3-lun7 u7 tiong-sin5 ti7-chia keng3 i cho3 tiong-sin5 chiu7 thang, chun i cho3 hong5-te3 chiu7 m7-thang; ho5-hong3 chun lang5 cho3 Siong7-te3 an2-chaiN2-iuN7 thang leh? Lang5 si2 sin kui-thou5, leng5-hun5 kui Siong7-te3 sim2-phoaN3. Na7-si7 ho2--e5, siuN2 i jip8 Thian-tong5, phaiN2--e5, hoat8--i loh8 te7-gek8. Ki3-jian5 li7-khui chit se3-kan kap lang5 bo5 kan-siap8; kiu3 lang5 hai7 lang5 e5 koan5-leng5 long2 m7-si7 i sou2 u7; sou2-i2 che3--i2 kiu5--i bu5 ek, ho7-hok e5 koan5 si7 Siong7-te3 teh chiang2. Na7-u7 beh kiu5 choan-choan tioh8 kiu5--i; na7-u7 tit-tioh8, chhim-chhim tioh8 kam2-sia7 i, eng2 be7 ke2-oaN7-tit e5 cheng5-li2.” 
  Lau7-lang5 mng7, “ThiN-te7 jit8 goeh8 hiah-e5 an2-chaiN2-iuN7 m7-thang pai3?” 
  In3 kong2,“Chit-e5 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 chhong3-cho7 e5 mih8, cho3 beh hou7 lang5 eng7--e5, m7-si7 beh hou7 lang5 keng3-pai3--e5. Eng7 e5 lang5 chiu7 tioh8 kam2-sia7 cho7 mih8 Chu2 Siong7-te3 e5 toa7 in-tian2. Liah8 mih8 cho3 Siong7-te3 toan3-toan3 m7-thang. Koh eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng kui I chhong3-cho7 e5 mih8, iah8 ban7-ban7 m7-thang. U7 chit8-e5 u-khu e5 thak8-chheh lang5, chiaN-goeh8 chhe-it, i-koan cheng2-che5, hoan7-na7 mng5, thang, chiN2, chau3, chhng5-tiuN3, i2-toh, long2 tioh8 ip-jia7. Lang5 mng7 i, i kong2, Bo5 mng5, be7 chhut-jip8; bo5 thang, be7 kng-beng5; bo5 chiN2, be7-tit-thang2 lim se2; bo5 chau3, be7-tit-thang chu2-chiah8; bo5 chhng5-tiuN3, bo5 tang3 thang khun3; bo5 i2-toh, bo5 tang3 thang che7. Chit8 ni5 e5 tiong-kan siu7 i e5 toa7 in, sou2-i2 tioh8 pai3 i.” 
  HaiN7 ah! ThiN-e7 thai2-tho2 e7 hiah che7 u-khu e5 thak8-chheh lang5 leh? Pang3-sak khi2-chhu3 hak-mih8 e5 Chu2 m7-chai thang kam2-sia7 i, khi3 ka7 chhu3 chham mih8 ip-jia7, kiam2 m7-si7 toa7 chho3-gou7? Siong7-te3 cho3 thiN kham3 lang5, cho3 te7 chai3 lang5, cho3 jit8 goeh8 chio3 lang5, cho3 ban7-mih8 iuN2-chhi7 lang5. Lang5 m7-chai chiah-e5 long2-si7 Chu2 phou-pai5 pou3-ti3 e5, beh hou7 lang5 thang eng7; hoan2-tng2 khi3 keng3-pai3 i, kap hit-ho7 pai3 chhu3, pai3 mih8 u-khu e5 thak8-chheh lang5 bo5 koh-iuN7.” 
  Lau7-lang5 thiaN-kiN3 chiam7-chiam7 beng5-pek8 chin-li2, cheng7-cheng7 siuN7 loa7-ku2, chiah koh-chai3 mng7 i kong2,“Goa2 sou2 leng2-kau3--e5 goa2 lioh8-a2 chai, tok8-tok8 lin2 kui3-kau3 bo5 keng3-pai3 chou2-kong chin7 put-kai.” 
  In3 kong2,“Ho2-tit li2 mng7 hit ku3. Goan2 e5 kau3 m7-si7 kim3 lang5 keng3-pai3 chou2-kong; si7 kim3 lang5 hok8-sai7 chou2-kong. Chou2-kong lim5-chiong e5 si5, kiaN2-sun tioh8 chin7 sim chiau3-kou3 hu5-chhi5, lai5 chou7 i-e5 sian7-chiong. Au7--lai5 iu7 tioh8 chin7 lat8 liong7-cha2 pi7-pan7 koan-kok i-khim ka7 i an-chong3, siong5-siong5 siau3-liam7 chou2-kong e5 in-cheng5, m7-kaN2 be7-ki3-tit. Sun7-than3 i sou2 lau5 e5 ho2 ka3-si7, m7-kaN2 ui5-keh8; hun5-bong7 na7 u7 phaiN2 tioh8 siu-li2. Che chiaN3 sit8-chai7 si7 teh keng3 chou2-kong. 
  Lun7-kau3 hok8-sai7 khi2 su5-tng5,chhai7 sin5-ui7, siat bok8-chu2, hiah-e5 su7 long2 si7 khang-hi lam7-sam2. Lang5 si2 seng-khu hiu2-noa7 ti7 thou3--nih8, ho2--e5, leng5-hun5 kui thian-tong5, phaiN2--e5, leng5-hun5 kui te7-gek8, be7 koh lai5 hiong2-siu7 che3-hian3 e5 mih8. Seng-le2, chhai3-png7, chiu2-sek8, pai5 moa2 toh-teng2, iu5-goan5 si7 oah8 lang5 teh chiah8, kang7 si2 lang5 long2 bo5 ti7-tai7. Na7-si7 chou2-kong tioh8 chiah8, siaN2-su7 che3-hian3 kin7--e5, bo5 che3-hian3 hng7--e5? Kiam2 m7-si7 hng7 e5 chou2-kong eng-kai iau-go7 mah? Iu7-koh chit8 ni5 che3-hian3 kui2-koe3 nia7-nia7, na7-si7 chin-chiaN3 tioh8 chiah8, chou2-kong kiam2 bo5 go7-si2 mah? 
  Iu7-koh tioh8 sio choa2-chiN5, bo5 siuN7 lang5 ti7 se3-kan u7 hek8-sin e5 heng5, chiah8 eng7 u7 heng5 e5 mih8. Sou2-i2 tioh8 chiN5-gin5 be2 chiah8, be2 chheng7, be2 khi3-khu7, lai5 iuN2-chhi7. Lang5 si2 liau2-au7 hek8-sin kui thou5 bo5 khiam3-eng7 mih8, leng5-hun5 si7 bo5 heng5 e5 mih8, be7-sai2-tit eng7 u7 heng5 e5 chiah8 chheng7. Na7 kong2 tioh8 khiam3-eng7 chiN5-gin5, eng-kai eng7 chin--e5 hou7 i, siaN2-su7 eng7 choa2-hu lai5 phian3--i? Choa2 si7 tek lai5 cho3-chiaN5--e5, ki3-jian5 sio-liau2 si7 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 choa2-hu, beh thai3-e7 piN3-cho3 chin-chiaN3 e5 chiN5-gin5 mah? 
  Iu7-koh che3-su7 si7 kou2-cha2 keng3 Siong7-te3 e5 le2, m7-thang lam7-sam2 kui7 ti7 lang5. Chong2-si7 keng3 chou2-kong si7 thiN-e7 thong-heng5 e5 toa7-lou7; hok8-sai7 chou2-kong si7 lang5 ka-ti7 khui e5 phian-phiah lou7; m7-na7 bo5-iaN2 e5 tai7-chi3, koh toa7 ui5-keh8 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7. Beng5-pek8 chin-li2 e5 lang5 tek-khak m7 an2-ni cho3.” 
  Lau7-lang5 kong2,“Che chin-chiaN3 si7 to7-li2 e5 oe7. Chiong5-cheng5 goa2 m7-bat thiaN-kiN3, kin-a2-jit8 kai-chai3 lai5 leng2-kau3, e7 hiau2-gou7 lah, lun7 chun-keng3 chham hok8-sai7 u7 hun-piat8. Sian-siN khui-thiah cheng5-li2 siong5-se3, thong lang5 e5 sim-khiau3 be7 chio2.” 
  Iau2 u7 chit8-ku3-oe7 beh chheng2-kau3. Goa2 taN chai ngou2-siong7 i2-kip8 it-khai3 se3-siok8 sou2 keng3 e5 sin5-beng5 long2 si7 tui3 lang5 e5 i3-su3 chhut--lai5; iah8 chai thiN-te7 jit8-goeh8 hiah-e5 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 chhong3-cho7 e5, keng3-pai3 i bo5 li7-ek, koh u7 toa7 choe7; iah8 chai Siong7-te3 si7 tok8-it e5 chin Chu2, ban7 se3 ban7 kok sou2 eng-kai tioh8 chun-chong5 keng3-pai3 i. Na7-si7 lun7-kau3 Ia5-sou, goa2 lau7-gong7 e5 lang5 iau2-boe7 hiau2-tit kau3 thiat-te2, goan7 sian-siN beng5-beng5 ka3-si7 goa2.” 
  Li2 sian-siN kong2,“Kiu3-chu2 Ia5-sou it-gian5-lan5-chin7, ke-lai7 u7 ‘Sin-iok e5 choan5-su,’kap‘thian-to7 sok-goan5,’chham‘Thian-lou7 chi2-beng5,’ ‘Tek-hui7 jip8-bun5’,‘Seng3-kau3 bun7-tap’, hiah-e5 chheh; iong5 goa2 leng7 jit8 toa3--lai5 chioh lau7-peh ka-ti7 khi3 khoaN3, chiu7 beng5-pek8 thau3-thiat. 
  TaN chhiaN2 iok-liok8 kong2 hou7 li2 thiaN, Siong7-te3 tok8-tok8 chit8-e5, na7-si7 it-the2 e5 tiong-kan u7 saN-ui7; chiu7-si7 Seng3-pe7, Seng3-kiaN2, Seng3-sin5. Ia5-sou chiu7-si7 saN-ui7-lai7 te7-ji7-ui7 e5 Seng3-kiaN2, tui3 chit8-chheng peh-pah peh-chap8-ji7 ni5 cheng5 Seng3-kiaN2 chhut-si3 cho3 lang5 lai5 kiu3-se3. Ia5-sou si7 Se-kok e5 im-gi2, hoan-ek8 chiu7-si7 kiu3-se3 e5 i3-su3, chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni Ia5-sou u7 nng7-e5 seng3, chit8-e5 Siong7-te3 e5 seng3, chit8-e5 lang5 e5 seng3. Chit nng7-e5 seng3 hap8 cho3-hoe2 lai5 chiaN5 chit8-e5 Kiu3-chu2. 
  Lang5 li7-khui Siong7-te3 tek-heng7 i2-keng soe-bi5, Ia5-sou lai5 ti7 i ka-ti7 e5 seng-khu chiong Siong7-te3 hian2-chhut hou7 lang5 khoaN3; hou7 lang5 koh-chai3 kap Siong7-te3 chhin-kin7, lai5 heng-khi2 in e5 tek-heng7. Se3-kan long2 ou-am3 m7-bat Siong7-te3 e5 chin-li2, khi3 kiaN5 sia5-lou7. Ia5-sou eng7 thiN-teng2 e5 kng lai5 chio3--in, hou7 in khi3-sia5 kui-cheng3. Se3-kan lang5 long2 u7 choe7, eng-kai siu7 eng2-oan2 e5 heng5-hoat8, Ia5-sou cho3 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2, chi3-chun chi3-kui3, ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2 the3 lang5 si2, siok8 cheng3-lang5 e5 choe7-ok, hou7 lang5 e7 bian2-tit tim5-lun5 e5 kan-khou2, lai5 tit-tioh8 eng2-oan2 e5 hok-khi3. 
  Chu2 si2 liau2-au7 saN jit8 koh-oah8, si3-chap8 jit8 seng-thian, che7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 iu7-peng5, chiang2 thiN-te7 ban7-mih8 e5 koan5; siuN2-su3 Seng3-sin5 lim5-kau3 lai5 kam2-tong7 lang5 e5 sim, lai5 in2 lang5 kui cheng3-to7. Thong se3 e5 chin-kng, tok8-tok8 chit8-e5 Kiu3-chu2 Ia5-sou nia7-nia7, hoan7-na7 sin3-kho3 i tek-khak e7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. Na7 mng7 che oe7 u7 sim2-mih8 pin5-ku3, goa2 chiu7-si7 pin5-ku3. Ia5-sou i2-keng kiu3 goa2 thoat-li7 choe7-ok, hiuN-li2 chhu3-piN chiau5 chai.” 
  ThiaN Li2 sian-siN chit-ku3-oe7, bo5 chit8-e5 m7 tim3-thau5 kong2 u7-iaN2. Lau7-lang5 koh mng7,“Seng3-sin5 sim2-mih8 i3-su3?” 
  In3-kong2,“Seng3-sin5 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 sam-ui7 it-the2 e5 te7-saN-ui7; i-e5 lou7-eng7 chiu7-si7 e7 chio3-kng an-ui3 kam2-tong7 lang5 e5 sim, hou7 lang5 chai choe7, chou7 lang5 hoan2-hoe2 ke2-piN3, sin3 Ia5-sou lai5 tit-tioh8 eng2-oah8. Na7 oa2-kho3 ka-ti7 e5 khui3-lat8 lai5 ke2-piN3 cho3 ho2, koat-toan3 be7-e7; tek-khak tioh8 oa2-kho3 Seng3-sin5 se2-chheng i-e5 sim, toan-chiaN3 i-e5 sim, chiah e7-tit tu5-khi3 ku7-te2 sou2 bak e5 la5-sam5, lai5 chiaN5 cho3 seng3 cho3 ho2.” 
  Koh mng7 sian-siN kong2,“It-the2 sam-ui7, kiam2 m7-si7 kong2 u7 saN-e5 Siong7-te3 mah?” 
  In3 kong2,“M7-si7 lah. Sui-jian5 u7 saN-ui7 put-ko3 si7 chit8-the2, phi3-ju7 chit8-e5 lang5 e5 tiong-kan u7 leng5-hun5, iah8 u7 hek8-sin, hap8 lai5 cho3 chit8-e5 lang5. Che kiam2 m7-si7 nng7-ui7 it-the2 mah? Kiu3-sit8 si7 chit8 lang5, m7-si7 nng7 lang5. Goa2 eng7 chit-e5 cho3 phi3-ju7, m7-si7 kong2 Siong7-te3 kap lang5 sio-siang7. Siong7-te3 pun2-the2 si7 sin5 bo5 heng5, bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5 u7 hek8-sin; put-ko3 si7 chioh lai5 piau2-beng5 it-the2, bo5 tek-khak chit8-e5, hek8-si7 nng7-e5 saN-e5 long2 thang. Che si7 kek8 o3-biau7 e5 cheng5-li2, kek8 chin-sit8 e5 tai7-chi3, na7 chhim-chhim sin3 kiam2-chhai3 thang lioh8-a2 chai.” 
  Koh mng7 kong2,“Chit-e5 to7-li2 kiam2 m7-si7 tui3 Sai-iuN5 lai5 mah?” 
